title: War of the Roses: He Was Supposed to be Going to Virginia but His Plane Ticket Said Otherwise
description: Brooke already knows her boyfriend Brian has cheated on her before and now her friend saw him on Tinder so she's ready to catch him red-handed.  And to add onto it all, he told her he was going on a trip to Virginia but the boarding pass she saw said somewhere else.  Is that somewhere else also where SOMEONE else is?
